::GoldenEye:;

She was completely dumbstruck. She had just met him and he was 
showing her great affections.  Not that she was complaining or didn't 
like, far from it.  But since this was her first real contact with 
another bot, she didn't know what to do.

"I..ah..I can..ah..hunt or...go with you to the...base..or..a.." 

Then he kisses her again.  She was flattered, but didn't know how to 
deal with this type of situation.  Combat, yes.  Fighting and 
stratagy, yes. Weapons, yes.  Kissing, not a chance.  There was never 
a manual in her old barreks that was on this.

She felt something inside her race and pound. It was her spark.  It 
was beating at what felt like light speed.
